{
  "title": "Deliciously Spicy Saudi Arabian Lamb Kebabs",
  "description": "A spicy and silky weeknight Saudi Arabian dish featuring lamb, jerk seasoning, and Mediterranean friendly flavors, with a hint of bonito shave for added depth.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
